@(206-208=c143.206) @q[Dumuzid,Belili]{“Old woman! I am not just a man, I am the husband of a goddess! Would you pour water -- please -- so I can drink water. Would you sprinkle flour -- please -- so I can eat flour.”}

@(209-212=c143.209) She poured water, and she sprinkled flour, and he sat down inside the house. The old woman left the house. When the old woman left the house, the demons saw her.

@(213-226=c143.213) @q[demons,self]{“Unless the old woman is aware of @wDN{Dumuzid's} whereabouts, she is indeed looking frightened! She is indeed screaming in a frightened way! Come, let us go to the house of Old Woman @wDN{Belili}!”} They caught @wDN{Dumuzid} at the house of Old Woman @wDN{Belili}. The men surrounded him and drained the standing waters. They twisted a cord for him, they knotted a net for him. They wove a reed hawser for him, they cut sticks for him, the one in front of him threw missiles at him, the one behind him ……. His hands were bound in handcuffs, his arms were bound in fetters. The lad raised his hands heavenward to @wDN{Utu}:

@(227-234=c143.227) @q[Dumuzid,Utu]{“@wDN{Utu}, you are my brother-in-law, I am your sister's husband! I am he who carries food to @wTN{E-ana}, I am he who brought the wedding gifts to @wSN{Unug}, I am he who kisses the holy lips, I am he who dances on the holy knees, the knees of @wDN{Inana}. Please change my hands into gazelle hands, change my feet into gazelle feet, so I can escape to the holy sheepfold, my sister's sheepfold.”}

